I have enough context to see the rough timeline: a 2014 target-driven sale process that terminates, then a 2015 New Mountain restart leading to execution and a go-shop. Before I write `events_raw.json`, I’m pulling the exact event schema from the live code and a cleaner block-by-block chronology dump so the artifact validates on the first pass.
